title: Geneva Volleyball Wins in Three Sets Over Grove City (Geneva College)
text: ( Source : Geneva College ) Beaver Falls, PA - Geneva beats Grove City in three sets (25-14, 25-14, 25-21) bringing the Golden Tornadoes to an overall record to 20-2, 10-1 in the Presidents' Athletic Conference . Erica Hughes ( North Jackson ,
